Hackathon to fine tune english to hindi language translator SLM
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
SLM used - https://huggingface.co/Helsinki-NLP/opus-mt-en-hi
Dataset  - https://huggingface.co/datasets/cfilt/iitb-english-hindi
training Arguments -
  batch_size = 16
  learning_rate = 2e-5
  weight_decay = 0.01
  num_train_epochs = 1
